-to-player-sentiment.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奇幻 Roguelike <em>Inkbound</em>的开发商 Shiny Shoe 宣布将从游戏中删除所有形式的游戏内货币化内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-mountain-goats-john-darnielle-talks-magic-the-gathering-secret-lair-set-3483851">山羊乐队的约翰·达尼尔 (John Darnielle) 谈论为《万智牌》写预言</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1062810/view/7306585773982973654?snr=1_5_9_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">游戏的 Steam 列表中发表的一篇文章</a>中，该团队辩称，最初将货币化纳入升级通行证和化妆品商店是为了支持游戏的开发。</p><p>此外，他们的目标是确保微交易“100％可选，仅用于装饰，对游戏玩法没有影响，并且没有 FOMO”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3515790" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515790" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3515790" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515790" class="wp-caption-text">一个人在游戏电脑上玩游戏 图片来源：Ella Don，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>然而，该公司表示，游戏行业的现状让 Shiny Shoe 得出结论，货币化并不是为游戏进展提供资金的流行方式。</p><p> “但是，很明显，行业和玩家的情绪正在与这些功能的存在背道而驰。因此，我们将完全取消游戏内的货币化，”该帖子继续说道。</p><p> “对于所有阅读本文并在游戏中购买过任何东西的人来说，真的谢谢你们。我们希望到目前为止您在<em>Inkbound</em>中度过了愉快的时光，我们将尽力在明年某个时候发布强大的 1.0。</p><p> “作为此次过渡的一部分，任何进行过购买的人都将获得额外的奖金奖励，以感谢您的支持。” </p><figure id="attachment_3515792" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515792" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3515792" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/indie-developer-removes-all-micro-transactions-from-game-due-to-player-sentiment-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515792" class="wp-caption-text">游戏电脑 图片来源：Ella Don via Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>因此，升级通行证中的内容将通过“Steam 上出售的仅限外观的可选“支持者包”DLC”提供。任何拥有《故事开始》或《恐怖星舰》高级通行证的人都将获得这些曲目中所有无人认领的奖励。</p><p>其余的化妆品内容和货币将在<em>Inkbound</em>中找到并通过玩来解锁。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，《龙之<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/like-a-dragon-gaiden-will-add-english-dub-after-launch-3515571"><em>龙外传：抹去名字的男人》</em>将于 11 月 9 日发售时，不会包含英文配音</a>。</p><p>这位<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indie-developer-removing-all-monetisation-in-inkbound-to-agree-with-player-sentiment-3515774">独立开发者取消了“Inkbound”中的所有货币化以同意“玩家情绪”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
