uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>即将发行的歌曲“Out of the Woods（泰勒版）”的片段出现在电影<em>《移民》</em>的预告片中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715"><b>“泰勒·斯威夫特：时代之旅”音乐会电影评论：这就是电影院（泰勒的版本）</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>备受期待的泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 2014 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-taylor-swift-15754-322720">《1989》</a>的重录版<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-1989-taylors-version-at-eras-tour-show-3480935">《1989（泰勒版）》</a>即将发行，该版本将于本月晚些时候发行。</p><p>现在，这位流行歌星在新动画电影《<em>移民》</em>的预告片中展示了她重新录制的歌曲“Out of the Woods（泰勒版）”的片段，对粉丝们对即将推出的版本的期待有了一些了解。</p><p>该剪辑于昨天（10 月 15 日）发布，是即将上映的 Illumination 和 Universal 电影的第三个预告片，并在后台播放了重新想象的曲目。 Illumination 的 YouTube 频道上有一句标语：“走出困境，但……尚未明朗”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《移民》预告片 3 (2023)“走出困境”泰勒版本" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CFWp9qtjPFY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这部电影由本杰明·雷纳执导，伊丽莎白·班克斯、卡斯帕·詹宁斯、库梅尔·南贾尼和奥卡菲娜等人配音。该片预计将于 12 月 22 日起登陆影院。</p><p>至于斯威夫特，《1989（泰勒版）》将于 10 月 27 日推出，此前还有《Speak Now（泰勒版）》等其他重新录制版本。后者于今年早些时候发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-scores-10th-uk-number-one-album-with-speak-now-taylors-version-3469052">标志着这位歌手的第十张英国冠军专辑。</a>它的销量也超过了其他前十名的销量总和。</p><p>上个月，斯威夫特透露了即将重新发行的“1989”的完整曲目列表，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-reveals-vault-track-titles-for-1989-taylors-version-release-3501247">包括几首“From the Vault”歌曲</a>。其中包括歌曲“Slut!”、“Is It Over Now?”、“Now That We Don&#39;t Talk”、“Say Don&#39;t Go”和“Suburban Legends”。</p><p>在一篇透露曲目的帖子中，斯威夫特写道：“这是一张新的原声带”，并补充道：“这是 1989 年（我的版本）的封底和金库曲目标题，我真的等不及这首了。感谢你们一起玩、调查、解谜，让这些揭示出更多混乱的乐趣（毕竟，这是最好的乐趣）。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxbFSR1RAOv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,